{"type":"message","id":"2dc9782f","parentId":"be35fcbb","timestamp":"2026-04-05T10:30:15.836Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Dark & Edgy:\nMy therapist told me I have a fear of commitment.\nSo I dumped her before she could say \"we need to talk.\"\n\nWorkplace:\nMy productivity hack is pretending my inbox is a black hole.\nNothing ever escapes, and eventually even my will to live gets pulled in.\n\nAbsurd:\nI asked my Alexa to play music that would help me focus.\nIt started playing audio of people arguing in a foreign language.\nTurns out I subscribed to \"Focus Can Be Found in Chaos\" on Spotify."}],"api":"openai-responses","provider":"openclaw","model":"delivery-mirror","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775385015834}}
{"type":"message","id":"3fd0c9ed","parentId":"2dc9782f","timestamp":"2026-04-05T10:33:43.445Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Conversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"message_id\": \"1140\",\n  \"reply_to_id\": \"1139\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"7924461837\",\n  \"conversation_label\": \"Nrexya id:-1003606834639\",\n  \"sender\": \"Nemesis\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Sun 2026-04-05 10:33 UTC\",\n  \"group_subject\": \"Nrexya\",\n  \"is_group_chat\": true,\n  \"was_mentioned\": true,\n  \"has_reply_context\": true\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"Nemesis (7924461837)\",\n  \"id\": \"7924461837\",\n  \"name\": \"Nemesis\",\n  \"username\": \"nemesis0008\"\n}\n```\n\nReplied message (untrusted, for context):\n```json\n{\n  \"sender_label\": \"Nexaaa\",\n  \"body\": \"Dark & Edgy:\\nMy therapist told me I have a fear of commitment.\\nSo I dumped her before she could say \\\"we need to talk.\\\"\\n\\nWorkplace:\\nMy productivity hack is pretending my inbox is a black hole.\\nNothing ever escapes, and eventually even my will to live gets pulled in.\\n\\nAbsurd:\\nI asked my Alexa to play music that would help me focus.\\nIt started playing audio of people arguing in a foreign language.\\nTurns out I subscribed to \\\"Focus Can Be Found in Chaos\\\" on Spotify.\"\n}\n```\n\nThis are not real jokes. Can u check top jokes and then send"}],"timestamp":1775385223437}}
