{"type":"message","id":"20fddd75","parentId":"6f6f3588","timestamp":"2026-04-05T10:34:06.852Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_e271f41ddd134ebb80dbfbe8","toolName":"web_search","content":[{"type":"text","text":"{\n  \"query\": \"best jokes 2024 top rated funny jokes\",\n  \"provider\": \"gemini\",\n  \"model\": \"gemini-2.5-flash\",\n  \"tookMs\": 16924,\n  \"externalContent\": {\n    \"untrusted\": true,\n    \"source\": \"web_search\",\n    \"provider\": \"gemini\",\n    \"wrapped\": true\n  },\n  \"content\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"4f6fac8d56e3f97e\\\">>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\nHere are some of the top-rated funny jokes from 2024:\\n\\n**From the Edinburgh Fringe Festival 2024:**\\n\\n*   \\\"I was going to sail around the globe in the world's smallest ship – but I bottled it.\\\" - Mark Simmons\\n*   \\\"I've been taking salsa lessons for months, but I just don't feel like I'm progressing.\\\" - Alec Snook\\n*   \\\"Ate horse at a restaurant once: Wasn't great.\\\" - Alex Kitson\\n*   \\\"I sailed through my driving test.\\\" - Arthur Smith\\n*   \\\"I love the Olympics.\\\" - Mark Simmons\\n*   \\\"My dad used to say to me 'Pints, gallons, litres' – which, I think, speaks volumes.\\\" - Olaf Falafel\\n*   \\\"British etiquette is confusing.\\\" - Chelsea Birkby\\n*   \\\"I wanted to know which came first the chicken or the egg, so I bought a chicken and then I bought an egg and I think I've cracked it.\\\" - Masai Graham\\n*   \\\"My girlfriend told me she's never seen the film Gaslight. I told her: 'Yeah you have… we watched it together.'\\\" - Zoë Coombs Marr\\n*   \\\"My aunty is Indian, German and a terrible human being. She's the curry wurst.\\\" - Raul Kohli\\n*   \\\"How do you know that Edinburgh is the most haunted city in the UK? You measure it with a spirit level.\\\" - Eleanor Morton\\n*   \\\"I recently read 10% of sheep are gay – turns out there's nowt so queer as flock.\\\" - Amy Mason\\n*   \\\"The Romans invented Vaseline. Or was it Ancient Grease?\\\" - Chris Turner\\n\\n**Other Funny Jokes and One-Liners from 2024:**\\n\\n*   \\\"Did you hear they arrested the devil? Yeah, they got him on possession.\\\"\\n*   \\\"What did one DNA say to the other DNA? 'Do these genes make me look fat?'\\\"\\n*   \\\"My IQ test results came back. They were negative.\\\"\\n*   \\\"Why can't you trust an atom? Because they make up literally everything.\\\"\\n*   \\\"Scientists have recently discovered a food that greatly reduces sex drive. It's called wedding cake.\\\"\\n*   \\\"I went to buy some camo pants, but I couldn't find any.\\\"\\n*   \\\"I was addicted to the hokey pokey, but then I turned myself around.\\\"\\n*   \\\"How do you make an egg roll? You push it!\\\"\\n*   \\\"When is a door not a door? When it's ajar!\\\"\\n*   \\\"What's red and bad for your teeth? A brick!\\\"\\n*   \\\"How do you make a tissue dance? You put a little boogie in it!\\\"\\n*   \\\"What do you call a pile of cats? A meow-tain!\\\"\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"4f6fac8d56e3f97e\\\">>>\",\n  \"citations\": [\n    {\n      \"url\": \"https://www.thenewdaily.com.au/life/entertainment/2024/08/20/fringe-festival-jokes\",\n      \"title\": \"thenewdaily.com.au\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"url\": \"https://www.whatsonstage.com/news/edinburgh-fringe-2024-top-15-jokes-revealed_49705/\",\n      \"title\": \"whatsonstage.com\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"url\": \"https://corporate.uktv.co.uk/newsroom/uanddaves-joke-of-the-fringe-2024\",\n      \"title\": \"uktv.co.uk\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"url\": \"https://www.theguardian.com/stage/article/2024/aug/12/10-funniest-jokes-edinburgh-fringe-2024\",\n      \"title\": \"theguardian.com\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"url\": \"https://www.rd.com/list/funniest-one-liners-you-havent-heard-yet/\",\n      \"title\": \"rd.com\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"url\": \"https://www.thelaw.com/threads/100-hilarious-jokes-because-no-one-is-too-old-to-laugh.83585/\",\n      \"title\": \"thelaw.com\"\n    }\n  ]\n}"}],"details":{"query":"best jokes 2024 top rated funny jokes","provider":"gemini","model":"gemini-2.5-flash","tookMs":16924,"externalContent":{"untrusted":true,"source":"web_search","provider":"gemini","wrapped":true},"content":"\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"4f6fac8d56e3f97e\">>>\nSource: Web Search\n---\nHere are some of the top-rated funny jokes from 2024:\n\n**From the Edinburgh Fringe Festival 2024:**\n\n*   \"I was going to sail around the globe in the world's smallest ship – but I bottled it.\" - Mark Simmons\n*   \"I've been taking salsa lessons for months, but I just don't feel like I'm progressing.\" - Alec Snook\n*   \"Ate horse at a restaurant once: Wasn't great.\" - Alex Kitson\n*   \"I sailed through my driving test.\" - Arthur Smith\n*   \"I love the Olympics.\" - Mark Simmons\n*   \"My dad used to say to me 'Pints, gallons, litres' – which, I think, speaks volumes.\" - Olaf Falafel\n*   \"British etiquette is confusing.\" - Chelsea Birkby\n*   \"I wanted to know which came first the chicken or the egg, so I bought a chicken and then I bought an egg and I think I've cracked it.\" - Masai Graham\n*   \"My girlfriend told me she's never seen the film Gaslight. I told her: 'Yeah you have… we watched it together.'\" - Zoë Coombs Marr\n*   \"My aunty is Indian, German and a terrible human being. She's the curry wurst.\" - Raul Kohli\n*   \"How do you know that Edinburgh is the most haunted city in the UK? You measure it with a spirit level.\" - Eleanor Morton\n*   \"I recently read 10% of sheep are gay – turns out there's nowt so queer as flock.\" - Amy Mason\n*   \"The Romans invented Vaseline. Or was it Ancient Grease?\" - Chris Turner\n\n**Other Funny Jokes and One-Liners from 2024:**\n\n*   \"Did you hear they arrested the devil? Yeah, they got him on possession.\"\n*   \"What did one DNA say to the other DNA? 'Do these genes make me look fat?'\"\n*   \"My IQ test results came back. They were negative.\"\n*   \"Why can't you trust an atom? Because they make up literally everything.\"\n*   \"Scientists have recently discovered a food that greatly reduces sex drive. It's called wedding cake.\"\n*   \"I went to buy some camo pants, but I couldn't find any.\"\n*   \"I was addicted to the hokey pokey, but then I turned myself around.\"\n*   \"How do you make an egg roll? You push it!\"\n*   \"When is a door not a door? When it's ajar!\"\n*   \"What's red and bad for your teeth? A brick!\"\n*   \"How do you make a tissue dance? You put a little boogie in it!\"\n*   \"What do you call a pile of cats? A meow-tain!\"\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"4f6fac8d56e3f97e\">>>","citations":[{"url":"https://www.thenewdaily.com.au/life/entertainment/2024/08/20/fringe-festival-jokes","title":"thenewdaily.com.au"},{"url":"https://www.whatsonstage.com/news/edinburgh-fringe-2024-top-15-jokes-revealed_49705/","title":"whatsonstage.com"},{"url":"https://corporate.uktv.co.uk/newsroom/uanddaves-joke-of-the-fringe-2024","title":"uktv.co.uk"},{"url":"https://www.theguardian.com/stage/article/2024/aug/12/10-funniest-jokes-edinburgh-fringe-2024","title":"theguardian.com"},{"url":"https://www.rd.com/list/funniest-one-liners-you-havent-heard-yet/","title":"rd.com"},{"url":"https://www.thelaw.com/threads/100-hilarious-jokes-because-no-one-is-too-old-to-laugh.83585/","title":"thelaw.com"}]},"isError":false,"timestamp":1775385246844}}
{"type":"message","id":"39f0b60e","parentId":"20fddd75","timestamp":"2026-04-05T10:34:14.415Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user asked me to check top jokes and then send them. I've found some jokes from web search. Let me select some of the best ones from the Edinburgh Fringe Festival 2024 and other sources to share with the group. These are real jokes that were popular.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning"},{"type":"text","text":"Here are some legit top jokes from this year:\n\n**From Edinburgh Fringe 2024:**\n\n• \"I was going to sail around the globe in the world's smallest ship – but I bottled it.\" - Mark Simmons\n\n• \"My dad used to say to me 'Pints, gallons, litres' – which, I think, speaks volumes.\" - Olaf Falafel\n\n• \"I wanted to know which came first the chicken or the egg, so I bought a chicken and then I bought an egg and I think I've cracked it.\" - Masai Graham\n\n• \"My girlfriend told me she's never seen the film Gaslight. I told her: 'Yeah you have… we watched it together.'\" - Zoë Coombs Marr\n\n• \"I recently read 10% of sheep are gay – turns out there's nowt so queer as flock.\" - Amy Mason\n\n**Other good ones:**\n\n• \"Did you hear they arrested the devil? Yeah, they got him on possession.\"\n\n• \"What did one DNA say to the other DNA? 'Do these genes make me look fat?'\"\n\n• \"Why can't you trust an atom? Because they make up literally everything.\"\n\n• \"How do you make an egg roll? You push it!\"\n\n• \"How do you make a tissue dance? You put a little boogie in it!\" 🖤"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"kilocode","model":"stepfun/step-3.5-flash:free","usage":{"input":1530,"output":403,"cacheRead":25472,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":27405,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775385246852,"responseId":"gen-1775385247-jrTpeMhiEvuiVQXQ5Zz3"}}
