arkles ✨, faces 😊🥺🥰, hands 🙌🤗)\\n• Often ends with a ❤️ or 💕 or 💞\\n\\nIt's basically: more emotions, more emojis, more \\\"I\\\" statements about feelings, more warmth, less bluntness. Does that help? 🖤\"\n}\n```\n\nChat history since last reply (untrusted, for context):\n```json\n[\n  {\n    \"sender\": \"Nemesis (@nemesis0008) id:7924461837\",\n    \"timestamp_ms\": 1775386827000,\n    \"body\": \"Give some more examples how indian feminine women talk in chat\"\n  }\n]\n```\n\nGive some more examples how indian feminine women talk in chat"}],"timestamp":1775386841703}}
