s you, happy for you)\\n✓ Ask about their day/feelings\\n✓ Use soft words (bestie, seriously, really)\\n✓ Exclamation marks — energy!\\n\\nWant me to send one tip like this every day around 3 PM? Just say the word and I'll make it happen 🖤\"\n}\n```\n\nYes"}],"timestamp":1775410873485}}
